title: Organic Select Deli and Mercado
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Ovo, American, Organic, Mexican, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Small organic market, deli, and bakery in a Vallarta midtown location since 2014; previously on Alameda. The kitchen makes salads, pizza, and soups. Has gluten-free pizza and bakery items, fresh juice bar, coffee and tea bar, and its own style of kombucha. Try the coconut milk latte. Wednesday is fresh farm produce day.
